NK011(da)004:0: phur pa rong lugs kyi dkyil 'khor cho ga bzhugs so //
NK011(da)004:1: bla ma dang dpal rdo rje gzhon nu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)004:2: phur pa'i las byang dngos grub rgya mtsho la mkho ba'i zur 'debs ni /
NK011(da)004:3: sa'i cho ga dang sta gon gnyis las /
NK011(da)004:6: gzhi bdag gi gtor ma mchod pa dang bcas pa bshams la /
NK011(da)004:7: bdag gi rnal 'byor sngon du 'gro ba /
NK011(da)004:9: ram yam kham gis bsregs gtor bkrus /
NK011(da)004:10: stong pa'i ngang las rin po che'i snod yangs shing
NK011(da)004:11: rgya che bar las mchod gtor rnams 'dod pa'i yon
NK011(da)004:12: tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa spro ba'i gter du
NK011(da)004:15: b+hu mi pa ti sa pa ri w+aa ra badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs /
NK011(da)004:16: ar+g+ham nas shap+da'i bar gyis mchod /
NK011(da)004:17: b+h+au mi pa ti sa pa ri w+aa ra na
NK011(da)004:18: mah sarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa sogs
NK011(da)004:19: lan gsum gyis gtor ma phu la la /
NK011(da)004:20: gang dag 'dir gnas lha dang klu //
NK011(da)004:21: gnod sbyin srin po'am gzhan dag la //
NK011(da)004:23: bdag zhu khyed kyis stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)004:24: zhes gsol bas spro ba dang bcas te sa gzhi byin par bsam la /
NK011(da)004:25: ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs su gsol nas gtor ma phyir dor /
NK011(da)004:27: lto 'phye brtags nas brkos pa'i sa ro rnams bsal
NK011(da)004:28: ba la stegs bu rtsig pa yin kyang btang snyoms
NK011(da)004:29: su byas nas sngags rgya tsam gyis sbyangs te /
NK011(da)004:30: dri dang ba byung sbyar ba'i chus dkyil 'khor gyi gzhir dbang ldan nas brtsams te byugs la /
NK011(da)004:31: ram yam kham zhes pas gzhi'i dngos 'dzin bsregs gtor
NK011(da)004:32: sbyangs nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i stong
NK011(da)004:33: nyid du bsgom / swa b+h+aa wa'i sngags bzla zhing
NK011(da)004:34: rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgyas reg par bya
NK011(da)004:35: nyid du bsgom / / gzung ba ni /
NK011(da)004:36: slob dpon dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi'i steng du 'dug ste /
NK011(da)004:37: bdag nyid rdo rje gzhon nu khro gtum bzod par dka' ba'i gzi brjid 'bar bar bsam la /
NK011(da)004:39: nyon cig bgegs dang zhes pa nas /
NK011(da)004:40: brgya ru khos kyi bar dang /
NK011(da)004:41: sum+b+ha'i drag basngagasa bzla zhing thun brab spos rol gyi
NK011(da)004:42: tshams rngams dang bcas te 'bar ba'i khro sprin g.yas
NK011(da)004:43: bskor du spros pas bgegs bskrad /
NK011(da)004:47: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum yig bcu yongs su gyur
NK011(da)004:48: pa las khro bo bcu smad phur bu 'bar ba'i
NK011(da)004:49: rnam pa can du bsam la /
NK011(da)004:51: khro bcu so so'i sngags mthar /
NK011(da)004:52: gnod byed 'byung po m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)004:53: ces btags pa bzla bzhin du btab /
NK011(da)004:54: bgegs rnams kyi spyi bo nas bsdigs pas gsang ba'i
NK011(da)004:55: bar du phug ste gser gyi sa gzhi la sbrags
NK011(da)004:56: nas g.yo 'gul med cing bde ba chen por ro
NK011(da)004:57: gcig tu gyur / srung ba ni /
NK011(da)004:58: steng yang phur pa'i bla re la //
NK011(da)004:60: rdo rje phur bu'i ra gur ye shes kyi me
NK011(da)004:61: 'bar bas phyogs mtshams thams cad du khyab par blta'o
NK011(da)004:63: bdud rtsi lnga dang ldan pa'i rak+ta chang dang sbyar te /
NK011(da)004:65: dus gsum rgyal ba'i bzhugs gnas khyad par can //
NK011(da)004:66: rang byung gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK011(da)004:67: lha srin sde brgyad tshogs rnams ma skrag cig /
NK011(da)004:68: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'di la chag chag 'debs //
NK011(da)004:69: khrag dang bdud rtsi'i kha phru 'di btab pas //
NK011(da)004:70: dus gsum bde gshegs thugs dam dbyings nas bskul //
NK011(da)004:71: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par shog /
NK011(da)004:72: ma h+aa dz+ny+aa na man+da la h+aum /
NK011(da)004:73: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi la khyem med par byugs /
NK011(da)004:75: slob dpon nub nas shar du phyogs pas /
NK011(da)004:76: bdag nyid rdo rje gzhon nu thig g.yog rigs kyi yum du gyur par bsam nas /
NK011(da)004:77: dza dzahzhesa thig sna gtad de /
NK011(da)004:78: rang gi lag g.yas kyi sor mo lnga la rigs kyi yab lnga /
NK011(da)004:79: g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK011(da)004:80: yab yum rjes chags kyis snyoms par zhugs pa'i mkha'
NK011(da)004:81: las thig skud byang chub kyi sems sprin dkar phreng
NK011(da)004:84: ye shes lnga yi skud pa 'dis //
NK011(da)004:87: mkha' la bde gshegs pho brang gsal //
NK011(da)004:88: +aahh+aum s+au tra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK011(da)004:90: de nas thig chal gyis sbags pa'i thig skud kyis /
NK011(da)004:91: tshangs thig nas bzung spyi dang mthun pa la //
NK011(da)004:92: phyi yi khor yug pad ra dur khrod bar //
NK011(da)004:93: cha phran phyed gnyis bskor ba dam can gnas //
NK011(da)004:94: rta babs bzhi ni mda' phyir cha chen gcig /
NK011(da)004:95: cha phran gcig ste de dag dum bzhir bgo //
NK011(da)004:96: de rjes g.yas g.yon 'don gyi brkyang bskum ni //
NK011(da)004:97: dang po ka rgyan mtha' las cha phran phyed //
NK011(da)004:98: ring zhing gnyis pa de las gcig gi thung //
NK011(da)004:99: gsum pa gcig ring bzhi pa gcig gi thung //
NK011(da)004:100: lte ba'i lha gnas rtsa ba'i thig nang du //
NK011(da)004:101: tshad mnyam zlum skor gnyis bskor gnyis ka'i nang //
NK011(da)004:102: cha phran gnyis bskor lte ba'i cha phran gyi //
NK011(da)004:103: phyi ru'ang de bzhin cha phran gcig gis bskor //
NK011(da)004:104: zlum bskor nang nas lte bar tshad pa des //
NK011(da)004:105: lte ba zlum por bskor ba'i nang thig dang //
NK011(da)004:106: nub kyi tshangs pa'i thig gnyis 'phrad mtshams steng //
NK011(da)004:107: 'gyang phur bzung la g.yas g.yon mtshan ma bya //
NK011(da)004:108: de dang shar gyi tshangs zlum phrad pa gsum //
NK011(da)004:109: bsgril ba'i chos 'byung mu khyud phyi nang dang //
NK011(da)004:110: rtsibs bcu rtsibs rten rnams su 'gyur ba'o //
NK011(da)004:111: de dag ni sa chog go //
NK011(da)004:114: bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba'i dri zhim po'i thig
NK011(da)004:115: le me tog gi tshom bu lha grangs dang mnyam
NK011(da)004:116: pa so so'i sngags kyis bkod mthar mchod pas bskor
NK011(da)004:117: / bdag gi rnal 'byor sngon du 'gro bas /
NK011(da)004:122: rdo rje gzhon nu bcom ldan 'das //
NK011(da)004:123: rigs sngags rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK011(da)004:124: sems can rnams la brtse ba dang //
NK011(da)004:125: khyed rnams la yang mchod pa'i phyir //
NK011(da)004:126: rdo rje 'dzin pa bdag gis ni //
NK011(da)004:128: rjes su brtse bas nyer dgongs te //
NK011(da)004:129: kun gyi byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK011(da)004:130: zhes lan gsum gyis snyan gsan dbab pas /
NK011(da)004:131: gnang ba byin par mos shing sngags rgyas dkyil 'khor nam mkhar bteg pa'o //
NK011(da)004:133: gtso las kyi bum pa gnyis chas su bcug bum rdzas dang bcas pa'i dri'i chus bkang /
NK011(da)004:134: dung zhal gzungs rdor dang bcas pa bshams la /
NK011(da)004:136: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i bum
NK011(da)004:137: pa mtshan nyid thams cad tshang ba yang shing rgya
NK011(da)004:138: che ba'i nang du pad+ma dang nyi zla'i gdan la
NK011(da)004:139: h+aum las dpal chen po khro bo bcu dang bcas
NK011(da)004:140: pa dang / las bum nang du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rnams skad cig gis gsal bar bsgom /
NK011(da)004:143: bdag gi zhal nas sngags kyi phreng ba gzungs thag
NK011(da)004:144: la brgyud de song ba bum nang gi lha rnams
NK011(da)004:145: kyi thugs kar thim par bsam la bzlas pa ci
NK011(da)004:146: 'grub bya / mthar lha thams cad chags pa chen
NK011(da)004:147: pos 'od du zhu nas byang chub kyi sems su
NK011(da)004:148: ro gcig tu gyur par bsam mo //
NK011(da)004:153: stong pa'i ngang las tshon rnams rigs kyi sa bon
NK011(da)004:154: lnga phyag mtshan lngar gyur pa las rigs lnga yab
NK011(da)004:155: yum bcur bzhengs pa rjes chags kyis sbyor bas zhu
NK011(da)004:156: ba'i byang sems ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin gyi rin
NK011(da)004:157: po che kha dog lnga'i rdul phra rab tu gyur
NK011(da)004:158: par bsam la sa bon lnga ci rigs bzlas te
NK011(da)004:159: byin gyis brlab / tshon thob ni /
NK011(da)004:160: chos 'byung sngo la zla gam khrag gi mtsho //
NK011(da)004:161: mu khyud dang po thod skam ra ba dang //
NK011(da)004:162: gnyis pa pad ma dmar po'i phreng bas bskor //
NK011(da)004:163: rtsibs bcu ser la rtsibs rten thod pa'i phreng //
NK011(da)004:164: rtsig pa nang nas sngo ljang dmar ser dkar //
NK011(da)004:165: 'dod snam la sogs spyi mthun rta babs bzhi //
NK011(da)004:166: dang po ser po gnyis dmar gsum ser po //
NK011(da)004:167: bzhi pa dkar po pad 'dab ris su bya //
NK011(da)004:168: sna tshogs rdo rje pad phreng spyi mthun la //
NK011(da)004:169: mu khyud khrag mtsho dur khrod rdo ra dang //
NK011(da)004:170: kha dog lnga ldan me ris bskor ba'o //
NK011(da)004:171: de dag ni tshon gyi las so //
NK011(da)004:173: phur bu byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK011(da)004:174: lcags snod 'bru nag gis bkang ba la lha phur
NK011(da)004:175: rnams bzhugs tshul ltar btsug pa mdun du bzhag la
NK011(da)004:177: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum las rdo rje sngon po h+aum gi mtshan pa re rer gyur /
NK011(da)004:178: gtso 'khor gyi sngags rnams tshar re brjod pas /
NK011(da)004:179: gtso phur rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum dang /
NK011(da)004:180: 'khor rnams khro bcu yab yum za gsod sgo ma
NK011(da)004:181: dang bcas pa thams cad stod rang rang gi khro
NK011(da)004:182: bo'i rnam pa rgyan cha lugs phyag mtshan dang bcas
NK011(da)004:183: pa la smad phur bu 'bar ba'i rnam pa can
NK011(da)004:185: gzi byin bskyed pa'i phyir gu gul gyi dud pas bdug la /
NK011(da)004:186: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya su ru su ru
NK011(da)004:187: pra su ru a d+hi sh+tha mugs mugs ha la
NK011(da)004:188: ha la dgra bgegs 'byung po tsit+ta myogs m+aa ra
NK011(da)004:189: ya h+aum phata / yungs kar gyis brab cing /
NK011(da)004:190: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ma gu ta la
NK011(da)004:191: ma gu ta la pra ta la sha da ra
NK011(da)004:192: tsa h+aum / dgra bgegs 'byung po m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK011(da)004:194: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya rak+ta dz+wa la man+da
NK011(da)004:195: la rak+sha rak+sha dgra bgegs w+aa sham ku ru m+aa
NK011(da)004:199: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK011(da)004:200: zhes sogs tshig bcad gcig gis gsol ba btab la /
NK011(da)004:201: chos sku 'gyur ba med pa'i ngang las gzugs sku
NK011(da)004:202: ye shes kyi khro tshogs phur bu'i rnam par byon
NK011(da)004:203: nas gnas so sor bzhugs par bsam zhing /
NK011(da)004:205: dbus na rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK011(da)004:206: bcom ldan rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK011(da)004:208: lha chen bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK011(da)004:209: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK011(da)004:210: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya dip+ta tsakra sa ma ya tish+than+tu /
NK011(da)004:213: phyogs bcu rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK011(da)004:214: khro rgyal yab yum za gsod bcas //
NK011(da)004:215: phyogs skyong pho mo'i gdan stengs su //
NK011(da)004:216: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK011(da)004:217: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra sa ma ya tish+tha n+tu /
NK011(da)004:218: zhes sogs khro bcu'i sngags kyis phyogs mtshams kyi khro bo brgyad rtsibs brgyad dang /
NK011(da)004:219: steng 'og gi khro bo shar nub kyi rtsibs nang thod phreng rtsar dgod /
NK011(da)004:221: ye shes gzhal yas sgo bzhi nas //
NK011(da)004:223: dkyil 'khor chen po'i sgo bzhi ru //
NK011(da)004:224: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK011(da)004:225: dzahh+aum bam hoh sa ma ya tish+tha n+tu /
NK011(da)004:226: zhes sgo khyud kyi nang bzhir dgod /
NK011(da)004:228: ye shes lnga ldan bum pa 'di //
NK011(da)004:230: chos kyi dbyings su sbyangs pa 'dir //
NK011(da)004:231: dngos grub stsol phyir bzhugs su gsol //
NK011(da)004:232: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bum pa stegs la dgod /
NK011(da)004:235: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK011(da)004:236: phun sum tshogs pa'i mchod sprin rab tu spros //
NK011(da)004:237: dpal chen 'khor bcas thugs dam gnyan skongs la //
NK011(da)004:238: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK011(da)004:239: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi sar du chu gnyis nyer spyod lnga /
NK011(da)004:240: lhor 'dod yon lnga dang bkra shis rtags rdzas sogs /
NK011(da)004:241: nub tu sman raka gtor gsum /
NK011(da)004:243: shar lhor las bzhi'i brang rgyas dang tshe 'brang dza
NK011(da)004:244: gad sogs dngos grub kyi rdzas sogs nyer mkho'i yo
NK011(da)004:245: byad thams cad 'tshogs par dgod do //
NK011(da)004:246: cho ga'i dngos gzhi ni las byang dngos grub rgya mtsho ltar dang /
NK011(da)004:248: rjes dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK011(da)004:249: nyon cig bgegs dang sogs kyi mthar sum+b+ha dang khro bcu'i sngags kyis bgegs bskrad de mtshams bcad /
NK011(da)004:251: gdal ba chen po chos dbyings sogs kyis byin dbab /
NK011(da)004:252: bdag dpal chen yab yum du gsal ba'i yab kyi
NK011(da)004:253: gsang gnas zla bar rdo rje rtse lnga gyis mtshan
NK011(da)004:254: pa / yum gyi mkha' pad+ma 'dab brgyad nyi mar
NK011(da)004:255: am gis mtshan par bsam la snyoms par bzhugs pas
NK011(da)004:256: yum gyi dung khang na khrag 'thung rigs lnga gnas
NK011(da)004:257: pa rnams bskul snyoms par zhugs pas yab lnga'i byang
NK011(da)004:259: yum lnga'i dwangs ma mtshal lta bu d+hu ti nas byung /
NK011(da)004:260: mkhar dkar dmar 'dres nas dngos grub kun gyi snying
NK011(da)004:261: por 'khyil ba yi ge gsum du gyur pa bdag
NK011(da)004:262: gi rdo rje'i nang du rngubs te thugs srog la
NK011(da)004:263: thim / bde stong 'dzin med rang byung gi ye
NK011(da)004:264: shes 'bar bar bsam la dkyil 'khor gsum gyi dzapa
NK011(da)004:265: thim / mthar / +aahh+aum sarba sid+d+hi +aah zhes btags pa ci rigs bzlas la /
NK011(da)004:266: k+aa p+aa la mtshan ldan du khrag chang a mri
NK011(da)004:267: ta dang mngar gsum sbyar ba 'bru gsum gyi byin
NK011(da)004:268: gyis brlab pa lag tu thogs te /
NK011(da)004:270: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu dang //
NK011(da)004:272: khro bcu yab yum za gsod dang //
NK011(da)004:273: sras mchog sgo bzhi srung mar bcas //
NK011(da)004:274: thugs dam dbang gis spyan 'dren na //
NK011(da)004:275: 'dir gshegs pho brang gnyan por bzhugs //
NK011(da)004:276: sa ma ya dzahh+aum bam hoh ho dpal chen yab yum 'khor dang bcas //
NK011(da)004:277: dang po chos dbyings ye shes lha //
NK011(da)004:278: bar du bdag gi yi dam lha //
NK011(da)004:279: da lta lha dang gnyis su med //
NK011(da)004:280: gnyis med rol pa'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK011(da)004:281: sman raka bdud rtsi sbyar bas mchod //
NK011(da)004:282: mchod 'bul rdzas sogs dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)004:283: zhes mtheb srin gyis gtor zhing so so'i mtshan sngags mthar /
NK011(da)004:284: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)004:285: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK011(da)004:287: de nas dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams thogs la /
NK011(da)004:289: srid pa'i phur bu bsgrub pa dang //
NK011(da)004:290: dbang dang dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK011(da)004:291: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK011(da)004:292: ye shes khro bo gshegs nas kyang //
NK011(da)004:293: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)004:294: rdorje phur bu'i lha tshogs dgongs //
NK011(da)004:295: dang po bsnyen pa'i dbu btsug nas //
NK011(da)004:296: do nub phan chad zhag grangs thengs //
NK011(da)004:297: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa'i grangs kyang tshang //
NK011(da)004:298: 'gro ba ma lus bsgral slad du //
NK011(da)004:299: k+ai la ya yi dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)004:301: / bcom ldan dpal chen yab yum sbyor //
NK011(da)004:302: gsang ba byang sems dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)004:303: phyogs bcu'i khro rgyal yab yum dang //
NK011(da)004:304: za byed gsod byed sprul pa bcas //
NK011(da)004:305: phyogs bcur dbang dang phyogs skyong 'dul //
NK011(da)004:306: dbang bcu yongs rdzogs dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)004:307: dpal chen sku gsung thugs las 'khrungs //
NK011(da)004:309: khro rgyal kun 'dus k+ai la ya //
NK011(da)004:310: khams gsum yongs grol dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)004:311: gser dngul zangs lcags lha phur bzhi //
NK011(da)004:312: bsnyen cing bsgrub pa'i lha lags kyi //
NK011(da)004:313: zhi rgyal dbang drag dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)004:314: dpal gyi bka' nyan sgrub mchog skyong //
NK011(da)004:315: shwa na bdag nyid sa bdag bzhi //
NK011(da)004:316: tshe dbang longs spyod grub rtags rnams //
NK011(da)004:317: mthu byin dregs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)004:318: bswe lcags dung gsum skyes bu ging //
NK011(da)004:319: ma bdun sring bzhi dbang phyug tshogs //
NK011(da)004:320: drag rtsal dngos grub rgya mtsho'i mdzod //
NK011(da)004:321: phrin las yid bzhin dngos grub stsol //
NK011(da)004:322: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya k+aa ya w+aa ka
NK011(da)004:323: tsit+ta a yu she r+dz+ny+aa na sarba sid+d+hi gu na
NK011(da)004:324: pha la hoh sid+d+hi sid+d+hi h+aum h+aum a a a
NK011(da)004:325: / zhes brjod cing lha dang dngos grub 'od du zhu /
NK011(da)004:326: bdag gi thugs srog la bsdu zhing dbyer med du gyur par bsam mo //
NK011(da)004:327: de nas smon lam gdab cing /
NK011(da)004:330: shis pa brjod cing rdul tshon chu bor gshegs pa'i bar bya'o //
NK011(da)004:331: rong phur las byang dngos grub rgya mtsho yi //
NK011(da)004:332: zur 'debs cho ga nyung ngur byas pa 'di //
NK011(da)004:333: rin chen rnam par rgyal bas bris pa'i dges //
